            "reviews": "“It manages to scratch that FTL itch while still feeling unique and its particularly enjoyable upgrading your ship with new modules then testing it out in battle. Highly recommended.”<br><a href=\"https://steamcommunity.com/linkfilter/?url=https://www.alphabetagamer.com/voidship-the-long-journey-alpha-demo/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"  >Alpha Beta Gamer</a><br><br>“I love the way you can actually build your own ship and I´m a big sucker for that random world FTL-ness of it all.”<br><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=URm-uV9wuLo&amp;list=PL6QTdQ_sjZI1_atCiX_E6JWTY6tUVOqAD\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer\"  >Nookrium</a><br>",
